$Id$

To build apg, run configure.  The configure script will determine
your system attributes and generate the Makefile from Makefile.in.
Next run make.  If everything goes fine, set your uid to root and
run make install.

user@localhost # ./configure
user@localhost # make

user@localhost # su root
root@localhost $ make install

